    "body": "![](http://channel.fritx.me/media/a2440363c680ba96e7a8282136586cf5.jpg)\n\n(This time I'm on Windows10 x64..) in main.js, seems alright..\nBut in index.html, the order of `module.paths` seems really bad:\n\n![](http://channel.fritx.me/media/fcac5e8aa5cff237147e40cf173095b7.jpg)\n\nAlso, this one is from before packaging, seems weird too..\n\n![](http://channel.fritx.me/media/9c96e3a179eef6b5766e162732e14bae.jpg)\n\n``` plain\n- test/\n  - hijack-demo/\n    - hijack-app/\n      - app/\n        - node_modules/\n        - main.js\n        - index.html\n```\n"
